name: Toccata and Fugue
description:
My transfiguration of Bach, entirely created by using his face as it was paint & brush, multiplied thousands of times, and finalized with AI enhancements to smooth and better define the myriad of glitches.

Explore the details of this 4096x4096 px artwork in this video: https://youtu.be/heN2lO7RWpE
